{"tid":221612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發威] 遺體脂肪太厚 火化火勢變猛釀火災","createTime":"2017-04-28T22:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T00:05:20.000Z","uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe73e0f89471c21680c6add00430b83e03e6172","tid":221612,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://metrouk2-files-wordpress-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/pri_37778576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2-files-wordpress-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2Fpri_37778576.jpg&h=afcb3f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國俄亥俄州一間殯儀館發生離奇意外，職員火化一具癡肥遺體時，火勢突然變猛，更擴散至火化爐外釀成火警；幸事件中無人受傷，火勢亦未波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n大火發生在周二晚，殯儀館負責人卡奇恩（Don Catchen）指，火化期間火勢變得強勁，令大火擴散至火化爐外，並燒著一個火化箱，「那具遺體屬癡肥，火化過程明顯比一般的更熱」。<br />\n<br />\n消防員表示幸火葬場做足防火措施，成功阻止火勢蔓延，事件沒人受傷，亦未有波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士指火化癡肥遺體有危險，是因為會出現俗稱「油脂火」，維珍尼亞州2014年火化一具500磅遺體時亦曾發生火警；奧地利在2012年火化一具440磅的女屍時亦引發火燭，令消防員「覆蓋着一層烏黑油脂」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《都巿報》/《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"b3cc7b1c7b685f7e4c25baffc5f700f94de60da3","tid":221612,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥婆死咗都想害人"},{"pid":"cac6f64311eda8c45adaaf5a149261dd161e05b1","tid":221612,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥婆死咗都想害人</blockquote><br />\nJack 下口德啦"},{"pid":"298c593682210c4b49262090e91561af332353ab","tid":221612,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:52:02.000Z","msg":"仲有冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b704821fc9dcf1844c03544270431120f1e1cc3","tid":221612,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T23:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屍油"},{"pid":"57a8a38098262be44f007a87f9f462cf59b05e7d","tid":221612,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:01:42.000Z","msg":"積屍油美帝波"},{"pid":"957f89cb11245e3a87b7bf524d82d9d0d9639df6","tid":221612,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:05:20.000Z","msg":"唔怪得肥就係原罪"}]}